  "body": "***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Text of message is not formatted accordingly on home screen when message in chat (1-1 / group / public) sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nText of message formatted on home screen in **bold**/_italic_ font when message in chat sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nText of message is not formatted on home screen in **bold**/_italic_ font when message in chat sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n![screenshot_20180204-143428](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/35777568-b6db0940-09b8-11e8-8a09-be1d00473b7b.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create 1-1 chat with Jarrad\r\n- Send message wrapped up with asterisks and tyldes (e.g. `*Bold*, ~Italic~ fonts`)\r\n- Navigate to Home screen and check if the text of the last message formatted with bold and italic fonts\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop (9f9155, 0.9.11d629), Release 0.9.13\r\n* Operating System: Android 7.0, Android 6.0, iOS (11.2.2)\r\n",
